com.SCHSRobotics.HAL9001.system.gui.menus

Class TelemetryMenu

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.SCHSRobotics.HAL9001.system.gui.HALMenu
      • com.SCHSRobotics.HAL9001.system.gui.menus.TelemetryMenu

  • public class TelemetryMenu
extends HALMenu
    A HAL Menu mimicking the normal built-in telemetry class. Has all the advantages of the HAL gui, however. This includes menu switching.
